abstract: >-
  HUF (Higgins Unity Framework) is a normalization-invariant audit layer for hierarchical mixtures
  (regimes/tenants/sources). It emits review-first artifacts (coherence map, active set, trace report,
  error budget) to diagnose dominance, concentration, and drift in multi-regime systems.

